about.summary: Interface to 'NatureServe' (<http://www.natureserve.org>). Includes methods to get data, image metadata, search taxonomic names, and make maps.
Interface to 'NatureServe' (<http://www.natureserve.org>). Includes methods to get data, image metadata, search taxonomic names, and make maps.

name: r-natserv
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-natserv
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/natserv_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/natserv/natserv_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 30f90f938e963191ef19b1433db1e265f67d8efe29c92a1d3603c3dc9a03d5c8

build:
  number: 4
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-crul >=0.7.0
    - r-data.table >=1.12.0
    - r-tibble >=2.0.1
    - r-xml2 >=1.2.0
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-crul >=0.7.0
    - r-data.table >=1.12.0
    - r-tibble >=2.0.1
    - r-xml2 >=1.2.0

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('natserv')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('natserv')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/ropensci/natserv
  license: MIT
  summary: Interface to 'NatureServe' (<http://www.natureserve.org>). Includes methods to get data, image metadata, search taxonomic names, and make maps.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
